#: app/templates/legal/privacy.html:63
msgid ""
"We retain your personal data for as long as your account is active. When "
"you delete your account, all personal data is permanently removed from "
"our systems. Financial transaction records are retained for the legally "
"required period (10 years under German tax law, AO Section 147)."
